---

## ğŸ§© Hybrid Design  

clinicalNLP does not rely solely on generative output.

It combines:

- Rule-based clinical heuristics  
- Deterministic signal construction  
- Structured LLM reasoning  
- Output schema enforcement  

This reduces hallucination risk and maintains consistent formatting suitable for regulated medical environments.

