## âš™ï¸ Setup  

```bash
git clone <repo-url>
cd clinicalNLP

python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt

uvicorn backend.main:app --reload
```

Test upload:

```bash
curl -F "file=@/path/to/ER_note.pdf" http://127.0.0.1:8000/upload-guideline
```

Run tests:

```bash
pytest
```

